{"word":"οὔπω","slug":"οὔπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὔπω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐ\">οὐ</a></el>, enclitic <el>πω</el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> particle indicating that an activity, circumstance, or condition is in abeyance or suspension, <b>not yet <a href='B:470 16:9'>Mt 16:9</a>; <a href='B:470 24:6'>24:6</a>; <a href='B:480 4:40'>Mk 4:40</a>; <a href='B:500 2:4'>J 2:4</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in J; <b><a href='B:530 3:2'>1 Cor 3:2</a>; <a href='B:570 3:13'>Phil 3:13</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:650 2:8'>Hb 2:8</a>; <a href='B:690 3:2'>1 J 3:2</a>; <a href='B:730 17:10'>Rv 17:10</a>.</b> Double <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> <el>οὐδεὶς <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὔπω\">οὔπω</a></el> no one ever <b><a href='B:480 11:2'>Mk 11:2</a>; <a href='B:490 23:53'>Lk 23:53</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οὖν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐρά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}